# Leveldesign Real Fake Game:
# ============================
# 
# The number-sign # introduces a comment.
# If placed at the beginning of a line, the line is ignored.
#
# Configure a level:
# -------------------
#
# T() means the number of tracks.
# B(background_img) loads the image file named "background_img.png". 
# M(bg_music) loads the music file named "bg_music.wav".
# D(10000) describes the length and duration of the level in frames.
# P(0.1) describes the pause between frames (here: 0.1 seconds; < 10 fps.)
#
# Example:
# L T(3) B(Backgnd001) M(Backgnd001music) D(2000)
#
#
# Introduce an enemy:
# --------------------
#
# "E": means enemy.
# "D": means the damage it can do.
# "S": means the speed it can move. S(1) means one pixel per frame in each direction, including diagonally.
# "A(example)": means animation. The files named example001.png, example002.png, etc. will be loaded.
# "N": means the number of enemies who will be spawned.
# "T": means the track upon which the swarm will be released (numbering starts at 0).
# "P": means the position within the duration in a level, meaning when, the enemies will spawn.
#
# This command creates an enemy with damage 1, speed 1, an animation cycle read from files named
# "EnemyA001.png", "EnemyA002.png", etc., creates 12 of them, and places them on the first track.
# E D(1) S(1) A(EnemyA) N(12) T(0)
#
#
# Introduce an obstacle:
# -----------------------
#
# "O": means an obstacle.
# "T": Describes to the right of which track it is. Meaning T(0) means it is between the first and the second track.
# "D": Describes at which point it appears (D like in Duration).
# "L": Describes how long it is (in duration points).
# "C": Describes the color. The syntax is "C(R,B,G)", where the three values show red, green and blue values for the colour.
# 		The values for R, G, B, must be between 0 and 255.
# "W": Describes the pixel width.


L T(2) B(background_tile_01.png,background_tile_02.png) M(Backgnd001music) D(2000)

E D(20) S(1) A(enemy) N(5) T(0) P(100)
E D(20) S(1) A(enemy) N(3) T(1) P(520)

BOSS D(18) S(2) HP(8) A(enemy) T(1) P(1750)

O T(0) D(100) L(100) C(35,56,90) W(5)
O T(1) D(560) L(100) C(70,160,90) W(5)
